  ('5df72fe8-b857-472b-b12c-cca73cc4ce1c-ex2', '5df72fe8-b857-472b-b12c-cca73cc4ce1c', 'entitle', 'The statute entitles every employee to paid sick leave irrespective of contract form.', '该法规赋予每位雇员带薪病假权利，不论合同形式。'),
  ('2e962006-476a-451a-ae2e-07cdb2091d8a-ex1', '2e962006-476a-451a-ae2e-07cdb2091d8a', 'evident', 'Her joy was evident to everyone.', '她的喜悦人人都看得出来。'),
  ('2e962006-476a-451a-ae2e-07cdb2091d8a-ex2', '2e962006-476a-451a-ae2e-07cdb2091d8a', 'evident', 'The conflict of interest was evident yet remained undisclosed for years.', '利益冲突显而易见，却多年未予披露。'),
  ('e1b3cdbc-9cd1-481a-90e2-56654ed7baa2-ex1', 'e1b3cdbc-9cd1-481a-90e2-56654ed7baa2', 'logic', 'There is a clear logic to her plan.', '她的计划有清晰的逻辑。'),
  ('e1b3cdbc-9cd1-481a-90e2-56654ed7baa2-ex2', 'e1b3cdbc-9cd1-481a-90e2-56654ed7baa2', 'logic', 'The majority''s logic, taken to its conclusion, would unsettle settled doctrine.', '多数意见的逻辑若推演到底，将动摇已经确立的法律原则。'),
  ('6d6d32ca-ac54-40c3-a5e1-54621411f863-ex1', '6d6d32ca-ac54-40c3-a5e1-54621411f863', 'essence', 'Honesty is the essence of friendship.', '诚实是友谊的本质。'),
