  ('a19c70cf-458c-40a3-a5b5-23c910410c6f-ex2', 'a19c70cf-458c-40a3-a5b5-23c910410c6f', 'motive', 'The court examined the motive behind the abrupt offshore relocation.', '法院审查了突然迁往离岸地背后的动机。'),
  ('85afae61-b41d-4b39-a7c1-2e6cd0895124-ex1', '85afae61-b41d-4b39-a7c1-2e6cd0895124', 'flood', 'The flood damaged many homes.', '洪水损坏了许多房屋。'),
  ('85afae61-b41d-4b39-a7c1-2e6cd0895124-ex2', '85afae61-b41d-4b39-a7c1-2e6cd0895124', 'flood', 'The disclosure unleashed a flood of regulatory inquiries across jurisdictions.', '这次披露在各司法管辖区引发了大量监管调查。'),
  ('4f2d6e3a-e6ba-4f76-84b6-a0b80cdbc933-ex1', '4f2d6e3a-e6ba-4f76-84b6-a0b80cdbc933', 'pen', 'Can I borrow a pen?', '我能借支笔吗？'),
  ('4f2d6e3a-e6ba-4f76-84b6-a0b80cdbc933-ex2', '4f2d6e3a-e6ba-4f76-84b6-a0b80cdbc933', 'pen', 'With a stroke of the pen, the decree nullified decades of practice.', '一纸法令大笔一挥，便否定了数十年的实践。'),
  ('07785b39-f1c5-4f6c-913a-305146171afd-ex1', '07785b39-f1c5-4f6c-913a-305146171afd', 'ownership', 'The ownership of the car is disputed.', '这辆车的所有权有争议。'),
  ('07785b39-f1c5-4f6c-913a-305146171afd-ex2', '07785b39-f1c5-4f6c-913a-305146171afd', 'ownership', 'The registry discloses the beneficial ownership of every domestic entity.', '登记系统披露每个本国实体的受益所有权。'),
  ('b818a5e3-1b01-4c30-a2e9-94ff42f14e5d-ex1', 'b818a5e3-1b01-4c30-a2e9-94ff42f14e5d', 'nightmare', 'She had a terrible nightmare.', '她做了一个可怕的噩梦。'),
  ('b818a5e3-1b01-4c30-a2e9-94ff42f14e5d-ex2', 'b818a5e3-1b01-4c30-a2e9-94ff42f14e5d', 'nightmare', 'The fragmented records turned the investigation into a logistical nightmare.', '零散的记录使这次调查成了后勤上的噩梦。'),
  ('4cdf7d53-de97-41de-8d45-0e7714cf6bca-ex1', '4cdf7d53-de97-41de-8d45-0e7714cf6bca', 'inspection', 'The car passed its annual inspection.', '这辆车通过了年检。'),
  ('4cdf7d53-de97-41de-8d45-0e7714cf6bca-ex2', '4cdf7d53-de97-41de-8d45-0e7714cf6bca', 'inspection', 'The inspection uncovered systematic falsification of the maintenance records.', '检查发现了维护记录被系统性伪造的情况。'),
  ('adb53cbd-c37a-4444-afb4-aab1f133bc72-ex1', 'adb53cbd-c37a-4444-afb4-aab1f133bc72', 'supervisor', 'My supervisor approved the leave.', '我的主管批准了休假。'),
  ('adb53cbd-c37a-4444-afb4-aab1f133bc72-ex2', 'adb53cbd-c37a-4444-afb4-aab1f133bc72', 'supervisor', 'The supervisor failed to escalate warnings that internal staff had repeatedly raised.', '监管者未能上报内部员工屡次提出的警告。'),
  ('1e6077d8-d351-43f2-8cc3-0753053d91aa-ex1', '1e6077d8-d351-43f2-8cc3-0753053d91aa', 'consult', 'Consult a doctor if symptoms persist.', '如症状持续请咨询医生。'),
  ('1e6077d8-d351-43f2-8cc3-0753053d91aa-ex2', '1e6077d8-d351-43f2-8cc3-0753053d91aa', 'consult', 'The agency must consult affected stakeholders before finalizing the rule.', '该机构必须在最终确定规则前咨询受影响的利益相关方。'),
  ('a292114e-274f-450a-9de0-99c6baecaa25-ex1', 'a292114e-274f-450a-9de0-99c6baecaa25', 'arena', 'The concert was held in a large arena.', '音乐会在一座大型场馆举行。'),
  ('a292114e-274f-450a-9de0-99c6baecaa25-ex2', 'a292114e-274f-450a-9de0-99c6baecaa25', 'arena', 'The dispute moved from the boardroom into the public political arena.', '这场争端从董事会议室转移到了公众政治舞台。'),
  ('5e076ebf-5c50-4f34-9f6e-2ca9a2871992-ex1', '5e076ebf-5c50-4f34-9f6e-2ca9a2871992', 'diagnosis', 'The diagnosis confirmed the illness.', '诊断确认了病情。'),
  ('5e076ebf-5c50-4f34-9f6e-2ca9a2871992-ex2', '5e076ebf-5c50-4f34-9f6e-2ca9a2871992', 'diagnosis', 'Early diagnosis dramatically improves the prospects for successful treatment.', '早期诊断能显著提高治疗成功的几率。'),
  ('920e4d2b-c0e5-4c2e-bf5f-ac5f2f440d69-ex1', '920e4d2b-c0e5-4c2e-bf5f-ac5f2f440d69', 'possession', 'The keys are in my possession.', '钥匙在我手里。'),
  ('920e4d2b-c0e5-4c2e-bf5f-ac5f2f440d69-ex2', '920e4d2b-c0e5-4c2e-bf5f-ac5f2f440d69', 'possession', 'The statute criminalizes possession of controlled materials without authorization.', '该法规将未经授权持有受管制材料的行为定为犯罪。'),
  ('95ce9e2a-bee7-4b1b-ba96-81f5ba349c80-ex1', '95ce9e2a-bee7-4b1b-ba96-81f5ba349c80', 'forgive', 'Please forgive my mistake.', '请原谅我的错误。'),
  ('95ce9e2a-bee7-4b1b-ba96-81f5ba349c80-ex2', '95ce9e2a-bee7-4b1b-ba96-81f5ba349c80', 'forgive', 'The creditors agreed to forgive a portion of the principal under the restructuring.', '债权人同意在重组中豁免一部分本金。'),
  ('17df5ca7-115f-4cc8-98bd-f43fe4009a7b-ex1', '17df5ca7-115f-4cc8-98bd-f43fe4009a7b', 'consistently', 'She consistently arrives on time.', '她总是准时到达。'),
  ('17df5ca7-115f-4cc8-98bd-f43fe4009a7b-ex2', '17df5ca7-115f-4cc8-98bd-f43fe4009a7b', 'consistently', 'The fund consistently outperformed its benchmark through unhedged currency bets.', '该基金凭借未对冲的货币押注持续跑赢基准。'),
  ('e2835030-5edb-49e4-9e41-511790514281-ex1', 'e2835030-5edb-49e4-9e41-511790514281', 'basement', 'The boxes are stored in the basement.', '箱子存放在地下室里。'),
  ('e2835030-5edb-49e4-9e41-511790514281-ex2', 'e2835030-5edb-49e4-9e41-511790514281', 'basement', 'The flood inundated the basement where the archives were kept.', '洪水淹没了存放档案的地下室。'),
  ('1ea3ecc3-3722-4e76-a3f2-9c0497d3c38a-ex1', '1ea3ecc3-3722-4e76-a3f2-9c0497d3c38a', 'drift', 'The boat began to drift away.', '船开始漂走了。'),
  ('1ea3ecc3-3722-4e76-a3f2-9c0497d3c38a-ex2', '1ea3ecc3-3722-4e76-a3f2-9c0497d3c38a', 'drift', 'The institution drifted from its mandate as oversight steadily weakened.', '随着监督逐步削弱，该机构偏离了其使命。'),
  ('bb6ddf42-8648-4ba6-93e5-f603d0eec7ac-ex1', 'bb6ddf42-8648-4ba6-93e5-f603d0eec7ac', 'drain', 'The sink won''t drain properly.', '水槽排水不畅。'),
  ('bb6ddf42-8648-4ba6-93e5-f603d0eec7ac-ex2', 'bb6ddf42-8648-4ba6-93e5-f603d0eec7ac', 'drain', 'Capital flight continued to drain reserves the central bank could ill afford.', '资本外逃持续消耗着央行难以承受的储备。'),
  ('87c6e85c-5525-4880-8b9f-2a73ba61b0cf-ex1', '87c6e85c-5525-4880-8b9f-2a73ba61b0cf', 'prosecution', 'The prosecution presented strong evidence.', '控方出示了有力的证据。'),
  ('87c6e85c-5525-4880-8b9f-2a73ba61b0cf-ex2', '87c6e85c-5525-4880-8b9f-2a73ba61b0cf', 'prosecution', 'The prosecution must prove every element of the offense beyond reasonable doubt.', '控方必须以排除合理怀疑的标准证明犯罪的每一构成要件。'),
  ('5950eaba-b27a-49a0-84d4-af567634631f-ex1', '5950eaba-b27a-49a0-84d4-af567634631f', 'maximum', 'The maximum speed is 120 km/h.', '最高时速是120公里。'),
  ('5950eaba-b27a-49a0-84d4-af567634631f-ex2', '5950eaba-b27a-49a0-84d4-af567634631f', 'maximum', 'The penalty may not exceed the statutory maximum absent aggravating factors.', '如无加重情节，处罚不得超过法定上限。'),
  ('2acbd2d6-ccb3-4603-b243-5d8f368e6fe4-ex1', '2acbd2d6-ccb3-4603-b243-5d8f368e6fe4', 'announcement', 'The announcement surprised everyone.', '这个公告让所有人都很意外。'),
  ('2acbd2d6-ccb3-4603-b243-5d8f368e6fe4-ex2', '2acbd2d6-ccb3-4603-b243-5d8f368e6fe4', 'announcement', 'The central bank''s announcement triggered an abrupt repricing of risk.', '央行的公告引发了风险的骤然重新定价。'),
  ('fa81fbef-9530-4bd1-91b1-464dc890f56b-ex1', 'fa81fbef-9530-4bd1-91b1-464dc890f56b', 'warrior', 'The ancient warrior carried a shield.', '古代战士手持盾牌。'),
  ('fa81fbef-9530-4bd1-91b1-464dc890f56b-ex2', 'fa81fbef-9530-4bd1-91b1-464dc890f56b', 'warrior', 'She earned a reputation as a determined warrior for consumer rights.', '她以坚定的消费者权益斗士而闻名。'),
  ('1b09360f-3226-4dca-8ee3-a3e2c42675d6-ex1', '1b09360f-3226-4dca-8ee3-a3e2c42675d6', 'prediction', 'His prediction came true.', '他的预言应验了。'),
  ('1b09360f-3226-4dca-8ee3-a3e2c42675d6-ex2', '1b09360f-3226-4dca-8ee3-a3e2c42675d6', 'prediction', 'No standard model''s prediction anticipated the correlated failures that ensued.', '任何标准模型的预测都未能预见随后发生的关联性失灵。'),
  ('aeedc864-9e84-49b6-86ab-205e40b47a82-ex1', 'aeedc864-9e84-49b6-86ab-205e40b47a82', 'bacteria', 'Washing hands removes bacteria.', '洗手能清除细菌。'),
  ('aeedc864-9e84-49b6-86ab-205e40b47a82-ex2', 'aeedc864-9e84-49b6-86ab-205e40b47a82', 'bacteria', 'Antibiotic resistance renders once-treatable bacteria increasingly lethal.', '抗生素耐药性使曾经可治的细菌日益致命。'),
  ('e39b8a9c-089a-4f3a-8f45-0a962fd08f6d-ex1', 'e39b8a9c-089a-4f3a-8f45-0a962fd08f6d', 'questionnaire', 'Please fill out the questionnaire.', '请填写这份问卷。'),
  ('e39b8a9c-089a-4f3a-8f45-0a962fd08f6d-ex2', 'e39b8a9c-089a-4f3a-8f45-0a962fd08f6d', 'questionnaire', 'The questionnaire was designed to elicit candid responses under anonymity.', '该问卷的设计旨在匿名条件下获得坦诚的回答。'),
  ('21192294-853d-4856-9989-50640931629c-ex1', '21192294-853d-4856-9989-50640931629c', 'mud', 'The car got stuck in the mud.', '车陷在了泥里。'),
  ('21192294-853d-4856-9989-50640931629c-ex2', '21192294-853d-4856-9989-50640931629c', 'mud', 'The campaign descended into mud-slinging that obscured the substantive issues.', '这场竞选沦为互相抹黑，掩盖了实质性议题。'),
  ('f3075877-4c33-4675-b65a-43dae0333005-ex1', 'f3075877-4c33-4675-b65a-43dae0333005', 'infrastructure', 'The city is improving its infrastructure.', '这座城市正在改善基础设施。'),
  ('f3075877-4c33-4675-b65a-43dae0333005-ex2', 'f3075877-4c33-4675-b65a-43dae0333005', 'infrastructure', 'The bill allocates substantial funds for the rehabilitation of critical infrastructure.', '该法案为关键基础设施的修复拨付了大量资金。'),
  ('c802b240-071e-4ec1-9eb9-d5ac35388292-ex1', 'c802b240-071e-4ec1-9eb9-d5ac35388292', 'hurry', 'There is no need to hurry.', '不用着急。'),
  ('c802b240-071e-4ec1-9eb9-d5ac35388292-ex2', 'c802b240-071e-4ec1-9eb9-d5ac35388292', 'hurry', 'The hurry to deregulate left systemic vulnerabilities unaddressed for years.', '仓促放松监管使系统性弱点多年无人问津。'),
  ('16d41342-a72b-41ad-b01e-45b65e28bc20-ex1', '16d41342-a72b-41ad-b01e-45b65e28bc20', 'privilege', 'It is a privilege to study here.', '能在这里学习是一种荣幸。'),
  ('16d41342-a72b-41ad-b01e-45b65e28bc20-ex2', '16d41342-a72b-41ad-b01e-45b65e28bc20', 'privilege', 'Privileged communications are shielded from compelled disclosure absent waiver.', '特权通信在未放弃的情况下受保护，免于被强制披露。'),
  ('a04a180f-e8d0-4747-8044-9853897853fb-ex1', 'a04a180f-e8d0-4747-8044-9853897853fb', 'temple', 'We visited an ancient temple.', '我们参观了一座古庙。'),
  ('a04a180f-e8d0-4747-8044-9853897853fb-ex2', 'a04a180f-e8d0-4747-8044-9853897853fb', 'temple', 'The temple''s heritage status forecloses demolition without ministerial consent.', '该庙宇的遗产地位排除了未经部长同意便拆除的可能。'),
  ('eb575865-ecb3-47bc-8f97-3b98e49eece9-ex1', 'eb575865-ecb3-47bc-8f97-3b98e49eece9', 'outdoor', 'We enjoy outdoor activities.', '我们喜欢户外活动。'),
  ('eb575865-ecb3-47bc-8f97-3b98e49eece9-ex2', 'eb575865-ecb3-47bc-8f97-3b98e49eece9', 'outdoor', 'The ordinance restricts outdoor advertising within the historic district.', '该条例限制在历史街区内设置户外广告。'),
  ('bc946ce6-996d-4621-88a0-5f49f41426e8-ex1', 'bc946ce6-996d-4621-88a0-5f49f41426e8', 'suck', 'The baby sucks its thumb.', '宝宝吮吸自己的拇指。'),
  ('bc946ce6-996d-4621-88a0-5f49f41426e8-ex2', 'bc946ce6-996d-4621-88a0-5f49f41426e8', 'suck', 'Rising input costs continued to suck the margins out of efficient producers.', '不断上涨的投入成本持续侵蚀着高效生产商的利润。'),
  ('11f8688d-ad62-4df2-beed-24b85c753518-ex1', '11f8688d-ad62-4df2-beed-24b85c753518', 'broadcast', 'The game was broadcast live.', '这场比赛进行了现场直播。'),
  ('11f8688d-ad62-4df2-beed-24b85c753518-ex2', '11f8688d-ad62-4df2-beed-24b85c753518', 'broadcast', 'The court enjoined broadcast pending resolution of the confidentiality appeal.', '在保密上诉解决之前，法院禁止播出。'),
  ('a522d53c-1ba1-45b2-9c77-5caaa2272d61-ex1', 'a522d53c-1ba1-45b2-9c77-5caaa2272d61', 'leap', 'The cat made a big leap.', '猫纵身一跃。'),
  ('a522d53c-1ba1-45b2-9c77-5caaa2272d61-ex2', 'a522d53c-1ba1-45b2-9c77-5caaa2272d61', 'leap', 'The discovery represents a leap forward in our understanding of the disease.', '这一发现是我们认识该疾病的一次飞跃。'),
  ('3f1015d9-6009-4319-9519-cd960e375a3c-ex1', '3f1015d9-6009-4319-9519-cd960e375a3c', 'random', 'She picked a random card.', '她随机抽了一张牌。'),
  ('3f1015d9-6009-4319-9519-cd960e375a3c-ex2', '3f1015d9-6009-4319-9519-cd960e375a3c', 'random', 'The study employed random assignment to isolate the causal effect.', '该研究采用随机分配以分离因果效应。'),
  ('5dc7cc0c-e1cc-417a-9ff6-c88870e490cf-ex1', '5dc7cc0c-e1cc-417a-9ff6-c88870e490cf', 'wrist', 'She wears a watch on her wrist.', '她手腕上戴着手表。'),
  ('5dc7cc0c-e1cc-417a-9ff6-c88870e490cf-ex2', '5dc7cc0c-e1cc-417a-9ff6-c88870e490cf', 'wrist', 'The regulator was accused of merely slapping the firm on the wrist.', '监管机构被指责对该公司只是轻描淡写地敲打了一下。'),
  ('e95c1abd-a8b8-4821-b875-8cec8385c257-ex1', 'e95c1abd-a8b8-4821-b875-8cec8385c257', 'curtain', 'Please draw the curtains.', '请拉上窗帘。'),
  ('e95c1abd-a8b8-4821-b875-8cec8385c257-ex2', 'e95c1abd-a8b8-4821-b875-8cec8385c257', 'curtain', 'The settlement drew a curtain over a controversy that had dragged on for years.', '这次和解为一场拖延数年的争议画上了句号。'),
  ('aeea06f5-e63c-41c2-910b-90c57204e104-ex1', 'aeea06f5-e63c-41c2-910b-90c57204e104', 'pond', 'There are fish in the pond.', '池塘里有鱼。'),
  ('aeea06f5-e63c-41c2-910b-90c57204e104-ex2', 'aeea06f5-e63c-41c2-910b-90c57204e104', 'pond', 'The discharge contaminated the pond on which the village depended.', '排污污染了村庄赖以生存的池塘。'),
  ('2c8c0f3b-7c7a-43f8-be04-89a1b6858ad8-ex1', '2c8c0f3b-7c7a-43f8-be04-89a1b6858ad8', 'domain', 'This subject is outside my domain.', '这个题目不在我的专业范围内。'),
  ('2c8c0f3b-7c7a-43f8-be04-89a1b6858ad8-ex2', '2c8c0f3b-7c7a-43f8-be04-89a1b6858ad8', 'domain', 'Standard-setting in this domain has migrated from states to private consortia.', '该领域的标准制定已从国家转移到私营联盟手中。')
INSERT INTO vocab_examples (id, vocabulary_id, word, sentence_en, sentence_zh) VALUES
  ('86c9d775-ebc1-4d0c-8ea3-40a6b1613f9e-ex1', '86c9d775-ebc1-4d0c-8ea3-40a6b1613f9e', 'guilt', 'She felt guilt for forgetting his birthday.', '她因忘了他的生日而感到内疚。'),
  ('86c9d775-ebc1-4d0c-8ea3-40a6b1613f9e-ex2', '86c9d775-ebc1-4d0c-8ea3-40a6b1613f9e', 'guilt', 'Guilt must be established beyond reasonable doubt before any conviction.', '必须排除合理怀疑地证明有罪，方可定罪。'),
  ('42f1f934-6d94-4c0f-b3e6-2761f06d6946-ex1', '42f1f934-6d94-4c0f-b3e6-2761f06d6946', 'cattle', 'The farmer keeps a herd of cattle.', '这位农民养着一群牛。'),
  ('42f1f934-6d94-4c0f-b3e6-2761f06d6946-ex2', '42f1f934-6d94-4c0f-b3e6-2761f06d6946', 'cattle', 'The disease prompted a precautionary cull of cattle across the affected region.', '疫情促使对受影响地区的牛实施预防性扑杀。'),
  ('1a561dac-0ff6-4be4-893f-0adb04baedba-ex1', '1a561dac-0ff6-4be4-893f-0adb04baedba', 'walking', 'Walking is good for your health.', '散步有益健康。'),
  ('1a561dac-0ff6-4be4-893f-0adb04baedba-ex2', '1a561dac-0ff6-4be4-893f-0adb04baedba', 'walking', 'The site is within walking distance of every major transit hub.', '该地点距各主要交通枢纽均在步行可达范围内。'),
  ('82211db8-632b-4c13-b8f9-d91f6a1435f4-ex1', '82211db8-632b-4c13-b8f9-d91f6a1435f4', 'playoff', 'Our team made it to the playoffs.', '我们队进入了季后赛。'),
  ('82211db8-632b-4c13-b8f9-d91f6a1435f4-ex2', '82211db8-632b-4c13-b8f9-d91f6a1435f4', 'playoff', 'The league restructured its playoff format to maximize broadcasting revenue.', '联盟重组了季后赛赛制，以实现转播收入最大化。'),
  ('80dd00f0-de5a-4ab2-8552-86cec9e0d420-ex1', '80dd00f0-de5a-4ab2-8552-86cec9e0d420', 'minimum', 'The minimum age to enter is eighteen.', '入场最低年龄为十八岁。'),
  ('80dd00f0-de5a-4ab2-8552-86cec9e0d420-ex2', '80dd00f0-de5a-4ab2-8552-86cec9e0d420', 'minimum', 'The amendment establishes a statutory minimum below which wages may not fall.', '该修正案设定了工资不得低于的法定下限。'),
  ('b82a14bf-8534-4bd3-b65b-0f0428852c54-ex1', 'b82a14bf-8534-4bd3-b65b-0f0428852c54', 'fiscal', 'The fiscal year ends in March.', '财政年度在三月结束。'),
  ('b82a14bf-8534-4bd3-b65b-0f0428852c54-ex2', 'b82a14bf-8534-4bd3-b65b-0f0428852c54', 'fiscal', 'Fiscal constraints foreclosed the countercyclical response economists urged.', '财政约束使经济学家所倡导的逆周期应对无从实施。'),
  ('d5241e28-9f20-46eb-9bf1-9e71e4fc8ac3-ex1', 'd5241e28-9f20-46eb-9bf1-9e71e4fc8ac3', 'skirt', 'She wore a long blue skirt.', '她穿着一条蓝色长裙。'),
