  ('f6326347-3f59-462f-9f52-4325f1747f94-ex1', 'f6326347-3f59-462f-9f52-4325f1747f94', 'ideology', 'The two parties have different ideologies.', '这两个政党意识形态不同。'),
  ('f6326347-3f59-462f-9f52-4325f1747f94-ex2', 'f6326347-3f59-462f-9f52-4325f1747f94', 'ideology', 'The reform transcended ideology, drawing support across the political spectrum.', '这项改革超越了意识形态，赢得了各政治派别的支持。'),
  ('eaab443c-c653-4c58-b837-1fea99c7a66d-ex1', 'eaab443c-c653-4c58-b837-1fea99c7a66d', 'tune', 'She hummed a familiar tune.', '她哼着一首熟悉的曲子。'),
  ('eaab443c-c653-4c58-b837-1fea99c7a66d-ex2', 'eaab443c-c653-4c58-b837-1fea99c7a66d', 'tune', 'The settlement ran to the tune of several hundred million dollars.', '和解金额高达数亿美元。'),
