  ('afc24e54-8d7e-41e1-ab0a-5030bba9331b-ex2', 'afc24e54-8d7e-41e1-ab0a-5030bba9331b', 'horn', 'The dispute placed the negotiators on the horns of an impossible dilemma.', '这场争端使谈判代表陷入了进退两难的困境。'),
