  ('32be1be3-83dd-435f-91a3-0951e4610003-ex1', '32be1be3-83dd-435f-91a3-0951e4610003', 'boost', 'The win gave the team a boost.', '这场胜利提振了球队的士气。'),
  ('32be1be3-83dd-435f-91a3-0951e4610003-ex2', '32be1be3-83dd-435f-91a3-0951e4610003', 'boost', 'The stimulus was designed to boost demand without stoking inflation.', '刺激措施旨在提振需求而不助长通胀。'),
  ('77de297e-51f2-47e6-84cb-83a80a10abba-ex1', '77de297e-51f2-47e6-84cb-83a80a10abba', 'bat', 'He swung the bat and missed.', '他挥棒落空了。'),
  ('77de297e-51f2-47e6-84cb-83a80a10abba-ex2', '77de297e-51f2-47e6-84cb-83a80a10abba', 'bat', 'The disease likely crossed to humans from a bat reservoir.', '这种疾病很可能从蝙蝠宿主传播到了人类。'),
