  ('f9ca7447-ae5c-495c-b3f6-02bc36de087f-ex1', 'f9ca7447-ae5c-495c-b3f6-02bc36de087f', 'festival', 'The town holds a music festival.', '这个镇举办音乐节。'),
  ('f9ca7447-ae5c-495c-b3f6-02bc36de087f-ex2', 'f9ca7447-ae5c-495c-b3f6-02bc36de087f', 'festival', 'The film festival showcased works grappling with displacement and exile.', '这次电影节展映了直面流离与流亡的作品。'),
