  ('b89dad89-afdc-460e-9a41-3546fc84d722-ex1', 'b89dad89-afdc-460e-9a41-3546fc84d722', 'freshman', 'She is a freshman this year.', '她今年是大一新生。'),
  ('b89dad89-afdc-460e-9a41-3546fc84d722-ex2', 'b89dad89-afdc-460e-9a41-3546fc84d722', 'freshman', 'The freshman legislator broke ranks to support the bipartisan compromise.', '这位新议员打破党派界限，支持两党折中方案。'),
  ('65a42743-4722-4dc4-86e9-7e0e587db080-ex1', '65a42743-4722-4dc4-86e9-7e0e587db080', 'sweat', 'He wiped the sweat from his face.', '他擦了擦脸上的汗。'),
  ('65a42743-4722-4dc4-86e9-7e0e587db080-ex2', '65a42743-4722-4dc4-86e9-7e0e587db080', 'sweat', 'The negotiators sweated the details of the verification annex for weeks.', '谈判代表花了数周时间在核查附件的细节上反复斟酌。'),
