  ('6ab51cb3-0077-4e10-b5f2-c63a4b405074-ex2', '6ab51cb3-0077-4e10-b5f2-c63a4b405074', 'drunk', 'Markets were drunk on cheap credit long before the inevitable hangover.', '在不可避免的宿醉到来之前，市场早已沉醉于廉价信贷。'),
