  ('439ed877-30e9-415a-821a-6aa35b5ff53d-ex2', '439ed877-30e9-415a-821a-6aa35b5ff53d', 'southeast', 'Investment surged across the southeast following the trade liberalization.', '贸易自由化之后，东南地区的投资激增。'),
