  ('7870372e-120a-47f9-bebb-095a961558c5-ex2', '7870372e-120a-47f9-bebb-095a961558c5', 'rhetoric', 'The pledges remained rhetoric unaccompanied by enforceable commitments.', '这些保证仍停留在辞令，没有可执行的承诺。'),
