  ('80f49d22-edef-43a2-8be9-8a19235eea64-ex1', '80f49d22-edef-43a2-8be9-8a19235eea64', 'enthusiasm', 'She greeted the news with enthusiasm.', '她热情地迎接这个消息。'),
