  ('6af3deeb-7de5-4933-bd48-927b42fca9f0-ex1', '6af3deeb-7de5-4933-bd48-927b42fca9f0', 'accommodate', 'The hotel can accommodate fifty guests.', '这家酒店可容纳五十位客人。'),
  ('6af3deeb-7de5-4933-bd48-927b42fca9f0-ex2', '6af3deeb-7de5-4933-bd48-927b42fca9f0', 'accommodate', 'The act requires employers to accommodate disability where reasonable.', '该法案要求雇主在合理范围内为残障作出便利安排。'),
  ('b590cdaa-f03f-48fa-b99f-f2b347c448fd-ex1', 'b590cdaa-f03f-48fa-b99f-f2b347c448fd', 'praise', 'The teacher praised her hard work.', '老师表扬了她的勤奋。'),
  ('b590cdaa-f03f-48fa-b99f-f2b347c448fd-ex2', 'b590cdaa-f03f-48fa-b99f-f2b347c448fd', 'praise', 'The judgment drew praise across jurisdictions for its meticulous reasoning.', '该判决以其缜密的说理赢得了各司法管辖区的赞誉。'),
