  ('e70a778d-40df-4d01-8d54-569c7a384471-ex2', 'e70a778d-40df-4d01-8d54-569c7a384471', 'mandate', 'The agency exceeded its mandate by imposing requirements never authorized.', '该机构施加了从未授权的要求，超越了其职权范围。'),
  ('8175eb41-46a4-4c85-9ff6-196b5cbd975a-ex1', '8175eb41-46a4-4c85-9ff6-196b5cbd975a', 'respectively', 'Tom and Amy are five and seven respectively.', '汤姆和艾米分别是五岁和七岁。'),
