  ('e2fc2b48-a4cc-4e13-a0ea-f961eb67ba84-ex2', 'e2fc2b48-a4cc-4e13-a0ea-f961eb67ba84', 'mechanical', 'Investigators concluded that mechanical fatigue caused the structural failure.', '调查人员认定机械疲劳导致了这次结构失效。'),
  ('28ba29e6-8972-402a-b232-85decb3bf76a-ex1', '28ba29e6-8972-402a-b232-85decb3bf76a', 'canvas', 'The artist painted on canvas.', '画家在画布上作画。'),
  ('28ba29e6-8972-402a-b232-85decb3bf76a-ex2', '28ba29e6-8972-402a-b232-85decb3bf76a', 'canvas', 'The inquiry painted on a broad canvas, examining a decade of practice.', '这次调查铺开了一幅宏大的图景，审视了十年的实践。'),
  ('e77de49d-d10e-4acb-bffe-e35c8f828506-ex1', 'e77de49d-d10e-4acb-bffe-e35c8f828506', 'forty', 'My father is forty years old.', '我父亲四十岁了。'),
  ('e77de49d-d10e-4acb-bffe-e35c8f828506-ex2', 'e77de49d-d10e-4acb-bffe-e35c8f828506', 'forty', 'Delegates from over forty jurisdictions attended the review conference.', '来自四十多个司法管辖区的代表出席了审议大会。'),
  ('8318d196-bd68-47cb-a893-fbeb4e4ae162-ex1', '8318d196-bd68-47cb-a893-fbeb4e4ae162', 'lobby', 'We waited in the hotel lobby.', '我们在酒店大堂等候。'),
  ('8318d196-bd68-47cb-a893-fbeb4e4ae162-ex2', '8318d196-bd68-47cb-a893-fbeb4e4ae162', 'lobby', 'The industry lobbied vigorously against the proposed disclosure mandates.', '行业对拟议的强制披露要求进行了大力游说抵制。'),
  ('0513d175-9892-4930-b1cc-155c954a47f5-ex1', '0513d175-9892-4930-b1cc-155c954a47f5', 'profound', 'The book had a profound effect on me.', '这本书对我影响深远。'),
  ('0513d175-9892-4930-b1cc-155c954a47f5-ex2', '0513d175-9892-4930-b1cc-155c954a47f5', 'profound', 'The ruling carries profound implications for liability across the sector.', '该裁决对整个行业的责任认定具有深远影响。'),
