  ('7faf93fe-887a-4423-b801-9fe46bf79969-ex1', '7faf93fe-887a-4423-b801-9fe46bf79969', 'thumb', 'She hurt her thumb opening the jar.', '她开罐子时弄伤了拇指。'),
  ('7faf93fe-887a-4423-b801-9fe46bf79969-ex2', '7faf93fe-887a-4423-b801-9fe46bf79969', 'thumb', 'The settlement was approved with only a cursory thumb-through of its terms.', '这份和解协议仅经粗略翻阅其条款便获批准。'),
  ('d99c9590-8ef5-4174-8995-b887840ff425-ex1', 'd99c9590-8ef5-4174-8995-b887840ff425', 'unity', 'The team showed great unity.', '这支队伍展现了高度的团结。'),
  ('d99c9590-8ef5-4174-8995-b887840ff425-ex2', 'd99c9590-8ef5-4174-8995-b887840ff425', 'unity', 'The bloc preserved a fragile unity throughout the contentious negotiations.', '该集团在整个争议性谈判中维持了脆弱的团结。'),
  ('b77e8e05-7e86-446f-b4d9-78ace70339ae-ex1', 'b77e8e05-7e86-446f-b4d9-78ace70339ae', 'compromise', 'We reached a fair compromise.', '我们达成了一个公平的折中方案。'),
  ('b77e8e05-7e86-446f-b4d9-78ace70339ae-ex2', 'b77e8e05-7e86-446f-b4d9-78ace70339ae', 'compromise', 'The compromise satisfied neither faction yet averted a damaging deadlock.', '这一折中方案两个派系都不满意，却避免了破坏性的僵局。'),
