  ('10adec95-250a-44c5-8c3a-d68b750d8abc-ex2', '10adec95-250a-44c5-8c3a-d68b750d8abc', 'horrible', 'The inquiry documented horrible conditions in the detention facilities.', '调查记录了拘留设施中骇人的条件。'),
  ('bcceea51-64a1-436e-89cc-c0dfd05eadea-ex1', 'bcceea51-64a1-436e-89cc-c0dfd05eadea', 'behavioral', 'The clinic offers behavioral therapy.', '这家诊所提供行为疗法。'),
  ('bcceea51-64a1-436e-89cc-c0dfd05eadea-ex2', 'bcceea51-64a1-436e-89cc-c0dfd05eadea', 'behavioral', 'The board imposed behavioral remedies rather than ordering full divestiture.', '董事会施加了行为性救济，而非责令全面剥离。'),
