  ('fe6dc24a-73f4-4ab8-9757-6046e870e0c8-ex1', 'fe6dc24a-73f4-4ab8-9757-6046e870e0c8', 'sidewalk', 'Don''t ride your bike on the sidewalk.', '不要在人行道上骑自行车。'),
  ('fe6dc24a-73f4-4ab8-9757-6046e870e0c8-ex2', 'fe6dc24a-73f4-4ab8-9757-6046e870e0c8', 'sidewalk', 'The ordinance assigns liability for sidewalk maintenance to adjacent owners.', '该条例将人行道维护的责任划给相邻业主。'),
