  ('3618e1b4-6ca5-46c4-a4d7-af2707076084-ex2', '3618e1b4-6ca5-46c4-a4d7-af2707076084', 'Olympics', 'The Olympics host committed to binding sustainability undertakings.', '奥运主办方承诺履行有约束力的可持续发展义务。'),
  ('90e4a489-b411-486d-8dd0-6224dec55163-ex1', '90e4a489-b411-486d-8dd0-6224dec55163', 'technological', 'Technological change is rapid.', '技术变革日新月异。'),
  ('90e4a489-b411-486d-8dd0-6224dec55163-ex2', '90e4a489-b411-486d-8dd0-6224dec55163', 'technological', 'Technological innovation continually outpaces the rules meant to govern it.', '技术创新不断超越本应规范它的规则。'),
  ('61c85b19-6dec-4b13-b3c3-79edfcf46117-ex1', '61c85b19-6dec-4b13-b3c3-79edfcf46117', 'signature', 'Please put your signature here.', '请在这里签名。'),
  ('61c85b19-6dec-4b13-b3c3-79edfcf46117-ex2', '61c85b19-6dec-4b13-b3c3-79edfcf46117', 'signature', 'The forged signature rendered the entire instrument void from inception.', '伪造的签名使整份文书自始无效。'),
  ('c1df1910-2381-454d-89b7-f3db3b154e21-ex1', 'c1df1910-2381-454d-89b7-f3db3b154e21', 'pleasant', 'We had a pleasant evening.', '我们度过了一个愉快的夜晚。'),
  ('c1df1910-2381-454d-89b7-f3db3b154e21-ex2', 'c1df1910-2381-454d-89b7-f3db3b154e21', 'pleasant', 'The deliberations were far less pleasant than the joint communiqué implied.', '实际的磋商远不如联合公报所暗示的那般融洽。'),
