  ('6d41d1af-dd2b-4fd0-b206-bea046f4f84d-ex1', '6d41d1af-dd2b-4fd0-b206-bea046f4f84d', 'rebel', 'The teenager began to rebel.', '这个少年开始叛逆。'),
  ('6d41d1af-dd2b-4fd0-b206-bea046f4f84d-ex2', '6d41d1af-dd2b-4fd0-b206-bea046f4f84d', 'rebel', 'Several backbenchers rebelled against the leadership''s whipped vote.', '几名后座议员违抗了领导层的党鞭指令。'),
