  ('b0fdf6a7-90b5-4fcd-98ec-03acb6abc865-ex2', 'b0fdf6a7-90b5-4fcd-98ec-03acb6abc865', 'carve', 'The exemption carved out an exception the legislature never intended.', '这一豁免开辟了立法机关从未设想的例外。'),
  ('49d5827c-3871-4a2c-8d95-c5db59ef7714-ex1', '49d5827c-3871-4a2c-8d95-c5db59ef7714', 'needle', 'Be careful with the needle.', '小心针。'),
  ('49d5827c-3871-4a2c-8d95-c5db59ef7714-ex2', '49d5827c-3871-4a2c-8d95-c5db59ef7714', 'needle', 'Finding the relevant clause was like searching for a needle in a haystack.', '找到相关条款无异于大海捞针。'),
  ('101ab2a6-3142-477e-96d5-10ba75b4e944-ex1', '101ab2a6-3142-477e-96d5-10ba75b4e944', 'belly', 'The baby has a round little belly.', '宝宝有个圆圆的小肚子。'),
  ('101ab2a6-3142-477e-96d5-10ba75b4e944-ex2', '101ab2a6-3142-477e-96d5-10ba75b4e944', 'belly', 'The venture went belly up once the promised financing collapsed.', '承诺的融资落空后，这个项目彻底破产了。'),
  ('e343f82e-c71c-4d6f-a4f5-4ad2abe852b6-ex1', 'e343f82e-c71c-4d6f-a4f5-4ad2abe852b6', 'scare', 'The loud noise gave me a scare.', '那巨响吓了我一跳。'),
  ('e343f82e-c71c-4d6f-a4f5-4ad2abe852b6-ex2', 'e343f82e-c71c-4d6f-a4f5-4ad2abe852b6', 'scare', 'The liquidity scare prompted a flight to ostensibly safe assets.', '流动性恐慌引发了向所谓安全资产的逃离。'),
  ('a2a6c512-b061-4cd5-902a-f7ad4d27698d-ex1', 'a2a6c512-b061-4cd5-902a-f7ad4d27698d', 'portfolio', 'He manages a large investment portfolio.', '他管理着一个庞大的投资组合。'),
  ('a2a6c512-b061-4cd5-902a-f7ad4d27698d-ex2', 'a2a6c512-b061-4cd5-902a-f7ad4d27698d', 'portfolio', 'The portfolio''s concentrated exposures amplified the eventual losses.', '该投资组合集中的风险敞口放大了最终的损失。'),
  ('49913299-bc62-40e2-aa16-b22c1018cd1d-ex1', '49913299-bc62-40e2-aa16-b22c1018cd1d', 'shuttle', 'A shuttle bus runs to the airport.', '有班车往返机场。'),
  ('49913299-bc62-40e2-aa16-b22c1018cd1d-ex2', '49913299-bc62-40e2-aa16-b22c1018cd1d', 'shuttle', 'Envoys shuttled between capitals to salvage the faltering accord.', '特使在各国首都之间穿梭斡旋，以挽救摇摇欲坠的协定。'),
