  ('c31affee-a2c1-4d33-aa41-da9adf7bf5ec-ex1', 'c31affee-a2c1-4d33-aa41-da9adf7bf5ec', 'counterpart', 'She met her counterpart from the other firm.', '她会见了对方公司的对等人员。'),
  ('c31affee-a2c1-4d33-aa41-da9adf7bf5ec-ex2', 'c31affee-a2c1-4d33-aa41-da9adf7bf5ec', 'counterpart', 'The minister conferred with her counterpart on the disputed border.', '这位部长与对方就争议边界进行了磋商。'),
  ('b55dc9bf-2984-4d3e-8c5e-8a0f03861bb9-ex1', 'b55dc9bf-2984-4d3e-8c5e-8a0f03861bb9', 'historically', 'Historically, the town was a port.', '这个镇历史上曾是一个港口。'),
  ('b55dc9bf-2984-4d3e-8c5e-8a0f03861bb9-ex2', 'b55dc9bf-2984-4d3e-8c5e-8a0f03861bb9', 'historically', 'Courts have historically construed penal exemptions narrowly.', '法院历来对刑事豁免作狭义解释。'),
  ('ce38f2ce-115e-4b85-8253-2272d32b4e53-ex1', 'ce38f2ce-115e-4b85-8253-2272d32b4e53', 'firmly', 'She firmly closed the door.', '她坚定地关上了门。'),
  ('ce38f2ce-115e-4b85-8253-2272d32b4e53-ex2', 'ce38f2ce-115e-4b85-8253-2272d32b4e53', 'firmly', 'The tribunal firmly rejected the jurisdictional objection as unfounded.', '法庭坚决驳回了被认定为缺乏依据的管辖权异议。'),
  ('ad2be66b-c4a2-4c15-a101-41d94a4ad985-ex1', 'ad2be66b-c4a2-4c15-a101-41d94a4ad985', 'mild', 'The weather is mild today.', '今天天气温和。'),
  ('ad2be66b-c4a2-4c15-a101-41d94a4ad985-ex2', 'ad2be66b-c4a2-4c15-a101-41d94a4ad985', 'mild', 'Even mild negligence may suffice for civil liability under the statute.', '根据该法规，即使是轻微过失也可能足以构成民事责任。'),
  ('466fd6c9-61f6-4bf9-835a-31259e842e76-ex1', '466fd6c9-61f6-4bf9-835a-31259e842e76', 'rider', 'The rider fell off the horse.', '骑手从马上摔了下来。'),
  ('466fd6c9-61f6-4bf9-835a-31259e842e76-ex2', '466fd6c9-61f6-4bf9-835a-31259e842e76', 'rider', 'An unrelated rider was attached to the bill in the closing hours.', '在最后时刻，一项无关的附加条款被塞进了法案。'),
  ('8df099d2-05a1-4acf-8bf6-9f31f90c636b-ex1', '8df099d2-05a1-4acf-8bf6-9f31f90c636b', 'doll', 'The girl played with her doll.', '小女孩玩着她的洋娃娃。'),
