  ('dcf05d89-0ba3-4a1f-841c-54cdcd13c223-ex1', 'dcf05d89-0ba3-4a1f-841c-54cdcd13c223', 'opposed', 'Many residents are opposed to the plan.', '许多居民反对这个计划。'),
  ('dcf05d89-0ba3-4a1f-841c-54cdcd13c223-ex2', 'dcf05d89-0ba3-4a1f-841c-54cdcd13c223', 'opposed', 'Several member states remained firmly opposed to extending the mandate.', '几个成员国仍坚决反对延长授权。'),
  ('dc319542-50c4-4ccc-b777-c4a34733b60d-ex1', 'dc319542-50c4-4ccc-b777-c4a34733b60d', 'orbit', 'The satellite is in orbit.', '卫星在轨道上运行。'),
  ('dc319542-50c4-4ccc-b777-c4a34733b60d-ex2', 'dc319542-50c4-4ccc-b777-c4a34733b60d', 'orbit', 'The smaller states were drawn into the orbit of the dominant economic power.', '较小的国家被纳入了主导经济强国的势力范围。'),
  ('15e16161-0f7c-40fa-92ff-e14eef08712a-ex1', '15e16161-0f7c-40fa-92ff-e14eef08712a', 'grasp', 'He has a good grasp of the subject.', '他对这门学科掌握得很好。'),
  ('15e16161-0f7c-40fa-92ff-e14eef08712a-ex2', '15e16161-0f7c-40fa-92ff-e14eef08712a', 'grasp', 'The full implications lay beyond the grasp of all but a few specialists.', '其全部影响只有少数专家才能领会。'),
  ('f1702883-c2ea-4d42-b787-c8c7b9508238-ex1', 'f1702883-c2ea-4d42-b787-c8c7b9508238', 'patience', 'Teaching requires patience.', '教学需要耐心。'),
  ('f1702883-c2ea-4d42-b787-c8c7b9508238-ex2', 'f1702883-c2ea-4d42-b787-c8c7b9508238', 'patience', 'The court''s patience with dilatory tactics had visibly worn thin.', '法院对拖延战术的容忍显然已所剩无几。'),
  ('0f56fba3-ddd6-4b45-a423-84486e38bb0c-ex1', '0f56fba3-ddd6-4b45-a423-84486e38bb0c', 'spite', 'He did it out of spite.', '他这么做是出于恶意。'),
  ('0f56fba3-ddd6-4b45-a423-84486e38bb0c-ex2', '0f56fba3-ddd6-4b45-a423-84486e38bb0c', 'spite', 'In spite of repeated assurances, the promised reforms never materialized.', '尽管一再保证，承诺的改革始终未能落实。'),
  ('e9917fcf-c442-4114-adf3-26364fd3754a-ex1', 'e9917fcf-c442-4114-adf3-26364fd3754a', 'tropical', 'They vacationed on a tropical island.', '他们在一个热带岛屿度假。'),
  ('e9917fcf-c442-4114-adf3-26364fd3754a-ex2', 'e9917fcf-c442-4114-adf3-26364fd3754a', 'tropical', 'The convention restricts trade in timber from protected tropical forests.', '该公约限制来自受保护热带森林的木材贸易。'),
  ('9dd432e6-5ffb-4ffb-8464-52e42178d094-ex1', '9dd432e6-5ffb-4ffb-8464-52e42178d094', 'voting', 'Voting starts at eight in the morning.', '投票上午八点开始。'),
  ('9dd432e6-5ffb-4ffb-8464-52e42178d094-ex2', '9dd432e6-5ffb-4ffb-8464-52e42178d094', 'voting', 'The founder retained voting control through a dual-class share structure.', '创始人通过双重股权结构保留了投票控制权。'),
  ('14004e8c-0d41-4e5b-9826-9abc84bdb663-ex1', '14004e8c-0d41-4e5b-9826-9abc84bdb663', 'patrol', 'A police patrol passed by.', '一支警察巡逻队路过。'),
