  ('971a5fa2-1c56-44b7-a390-a0f6c338a1e0-ex1', '971a5fa2-1c56-44b7-a390-a0f6c338a1e0', 'willingness', 'Her willingness to help impressed us.', '她乐于助人的态度打动了我们。'),
  ('971a5fa2-1c56-44b7-a390-a0f6c338a1e0-ex2', '971a5fa2-1c56-44b7-a390-a0f6c338a1e0', 'willingness', 'The settlement reflected a mutual willingness to avoid protracted litigation.', '和解反映了双方避免旷日持久诉讼的共同意愿。'),
  ('30d1ddd3-c663-4ccf-ad72-e621065fc3b5-ex1', '30d1ddd3-c663-4ccf-ad72-e621065fc3b5', 'revelation', 'The news was a shocking revelation.', '这个消息是个惊人的爆料。'),
  ('30d1ddd3-c663-4ccf-ad72-e621065fc3b5-ex2', '30d1ddd3-c663-4ccf-ad72-e621065fc3b5', 'revelation', 'The revelations prompted parallel inquiries across three jurisdictions.', '这些爆料引发了三个司法管辖区的并行调查。'),
  ('78f10b7e-bdbf-47be-b41d-d113ea664ca7-ex1', '78f10b7e-bdbf-47be-b41d-d113ea664ca7', 'calm', 'Stay calm and breathe slowly.', '保持冷静，慢慢呼吸。'),
  ('78f10b7e-bdbf-47be-b41d-d113ea664ca7-ex2', '78f10b7e-bdbf-47be-b41d-d113ea664ca7', 'calm', 'The deceptive calm in markets masked accumulating systemic stress.', '市场表面的平静掩盖了不断累积的系统性压力。'),
  ('314cf1ef-53c4-479a-8e8d-8edd268c6522-ex1', '314cf1ef-53c4-479a-8e8d-8edd268c6522', 'jewelry', 'She wore expensive jewelry.', '她戴着昂贵的珠宝。'),
  ('314cf1ef-53c4-479a-8e8d-8edd268c6522-ex2', '314cf1ef-53c4-479a-8e8d-8edd268c6522', 'jewelry', 'The seized jewelry was traced to the proceeds of the fraudulent scheme.', '查获的珠宝被追溯为欺诈方案的所得。'),
  ('095608fc-a395-4f36-b243-7f606a84e9c3-ex1', '095608fc-a395-4f36-b243-7f606a84e9c3', 'Cuban', 'We listened to Cuban music.', '我们听了古巴音乐。'),
  ('095608fc-a395-4f36-b243-7f606a84e9c3-ex2', '095608fc-a395-4f36-b243-7f606a84e9c3', 'Cuban', 'Cuban negotiators pressed for the lifting of long-standing trade restrictions.', '古巴谈判代表敦促解除长期存在的贸易限制。'),
  ('cf7cacc6-a6a9-4536-95d0-90aab7b47cca-ex1', 'cf7cacc6-a6a9-4536-95d0-90aab7b47cca', 'haul', 'They hauled the boat onto the shore.', '他们把船拖上了岸。'),
  ('cf7cacc6-a6a9-4536-95d0-90aab7b47cca-ex2', 'cf7cacc6-a6a9-4536-95d0-90aab7b47cca', 'haul', 'Recovering the assets promised to be a long haul across multiple jurisdictions.', '追回这些资产注定是一场横跨多个司法管辖区的持久战。'),
  ('001b1d49-9655-4417-8b3f-ae779a782a6e-ex1', '001b1d49-9655-4417-8b3f-ae779a782a6e', 'concede', 'He conceded that he was wrong.', '他承认自己错了。'),
  ('001b1d49-9655-4417-8b3f-ae779a782a6e-ex2', '001b1d49-9655-4417-8b3f-ae779a782a6e', 'concede', 'Even the policy''s defenders concede its fiscal assumptions were optimistic.', '连该政策的辩护者也承认其财政假设过于乐观。'),
