  ('81a58b72-ad66-4219-8b8d-66fcdd366b92-ex2', '81a58b72-ad66-4219-8b8d-66fcdd366b92', 'wagon', 'Several jurisdictions jumped on the regulatory bandwagon once enforcement intensified.', '执法力度加大后，几个司法管辖区也随大流加强了监管。'),
