  ('880b862e-0307-43cf-8536-a6b7868e62da-ex2', '880b862e-0307-43cf-8536-a6b7868e62da', 'afterward', 'The full implications became apparent only years afterward.', '其全部影响直到数年之后才显现出来。'),
  ('fdb5593c-3fe6-4fa0-8317-cffac9e39553-ex1', 'fdb5593c-3fe6-4fa0-8317-cffac9e39553', 'spectacular', 'The fireworks were spectacular.', '烟花表演十分壮观。'),
  ('fdb5593c-3fe6-4fa0-8317-cffac9e39553-ex2', 'fdb5593c-3fe6-4fa0-8317-cffac9e39553', 'spectacular', 'The spectacular collapse exposed risks supervisors had long ignored.', '这场惊人的崩溃暴露了监管者长期忽视的风险。'),
  ('b9cc23d3-2398-48e6-bbd5-62d30e01b41c-ex1', 'b9cc23d3-2398-48e6-bbd5-62d30e01b41c', 'ruin', 'The rain ruined our picnic.', '雨毁了我们的野餐。'),
  ('b9cc23d3-2398-48e6-bbd5-62d30e01b41c-ex2', 'b9cc23d3-2398-48e6-bbd5-62d30e01b41c', 'ruin', 'The scandal threatened to ruin a reputation built over decades.', '这桩丑闻可能毁掉数十年积累的声誉。'),
  ('fe496f7c-2ecf-4d81-b9be-5e68733bd5a4-ex1', 'fe496f7c-2ecf-4d81-b9be-5e68733bd5a4', 'sheer', 'It was sheer luck.', '那纯属运气。'),
  ('fe496f7c-2ecf-4d81-b9be-5e68733bd5a4-ex2', 'fe496f7c-2ecf-4d81-b9be-5e68733bd5a4', 'sheer', 'The sheer scale of the settlement reflected the gravity of the misconduct.', '和解金额之巨反映了不当行为的严重程度。'),
  ('7586a5bb-cf96-40f9-a478-1ee52dcb1d94-ex1', '7586a5bb-cf96-40f9-a478-1ee52dcb1d94', 'immune', 'She is immune to the disease.', '她对这种疾病免疫。'),
