  ('8948f601-4c92-44cf-8f4c-214fb4468a26-ex1', '8948f601-4c92-44cf-8f4c-214fb4468a26', 'reliability', 'The car is known for its reliability.', '这辆车以可靠性著称。'),
  ('8948f601-4c92-44cf-8f4c-214fb4468a26-ex2', '8948f601-4c92-44cf-8f4c-214fb4468a26', 'reliability', 'The defense challenged the reliability of the contested forensic evidence.', '辩方质疑有争议法医证据的可靠性。'),
  ('7dd08301-6444-4878-8305-259a824d41ee-ex1', '7dd08301-6444-4878-8305-259a824d41ee', 'ass', 'Don''t be an ass about it.', '别为这事犯傻。'),
  ('7dd08301-6444-4878-8305-259a824d41ee-ex2', '7dd08301-6444-4878-8305-259a824d41ee', 'ass', 'The board made an ass of itself by certifying figures any audit would disown.', '董事会签署了任何审计都会否认的数字，自取其辱。'),
  ('f16c2ea2-037b-48c5-9858-8fbf97c22efb-ex1', 'f16c2ea2-037b-48c5-9858-8fbf97c22efb', 'alongside', 'She walked alongside her friend.', '她和朋友并肩走着。'),
  ('f16c2ea2-037b-48c5-9858-8fbf97c22efb-ex2', 'f16c2ea2-037b-48c5-9858-8fbf97c22efb', 'alongside', 'The private auditor operates alongside, not in lieu of, statutory oversight.', '私营审计机构与法定监督并行，而非取而代之。'),
  ('00e2b4c2-71ea-4ae6-ad9b-89e13dea4cda-ex1', '00e2b4c2-71ea-4ae6-ad9b-89e13dea4cda', 'bush', 'A rabbit hid in the bush.', '一只兔子藏在灌木丛里。'),
  ('00e2b4c2-71ea-4ae6-ad9b-89e13dea4cda-ex2', '00e2b4c2-71ea-4ae6-ad9b-89e13dea4cda', 'bush', 'The minister beat around the bush rather than addressing the procurement question.', '部长拐弯抹角，而不正面回应采购问题。'),
  ('dcb96731-11c2-4842-bfae-ebfddc44e185-ex1', 'dcb96731-11c2-4842-bfae-ebfddc44e185', 'exotic', 'The market sells exotic fruits.', '市场出售各种珍奇水果。'),
  ('dcb96731-11c2-4842-bfae-ebfddc44e185-ex2', 'dcb96731-11c2-4842-bfae-ebfddc44e185', 'exotic', 'The portfolio held exotic instruments few investors could properly evaluate.', '该投资组合持有的奇异工具很少有投资者能正确评估。'),
  ('6219adb2-488a-4105-9edc-5652ae826e5e-ex1', '6219adb2-488a-4105-9edc-5652ae826e5e', 'fascinating', 'The documentary was fascinating.', '这部纪录片引人入胜。'),
