  ('373611aa-f748-42ca-a3a8-7f4f035a108b-ex2', '373611aa-f748-42ca-a3a8-7f4f035a108b', 'clip', 'The leaked clip captured deliberations the participants believed confidential.', '泄露的片段记录了与会者自以为保密的商议。'),
  ('e57b5612-c95a-4c21-b8fd-0f60bc900b11-ex1', 'e57b5612-c95a-4c21-b8fd-0f60bc900b11', 'thigh', 'He pulled a muscle in his thigh.', '他大腿拉伤了。'),
  ('e57b5612-c95a-4c21-b8fd-0f60bc900b11-ex2', 'e57b5612-c95a-4c21-b8fd-0f60bc900b11', 'thigh', 'The injury to his thigh ended a career at its athletic peak.', '大腿的伤病使他在运动巅峰期结束了职业生涯。'),
  ('740399bc-c865-434d-99c8-e6dab250df3b-ex1', '740399bc-c865-434d-99c8-e6dab250df3b', 'bull', 'The bull charged at the gate.', '公牛朝栅栏冲去。'),
  ('740399bc-c865-434d-99c8-e6dab250df3b-ex2', '740399bc-c865-434d-99c8-e6dab250df3b', 'bull', 'The prolonged bull market lulled investors into a dangerous complacency.', '持续的牛市使投资者陷入了危险的自满。'),
  ('c6601e80-b1b2-4eb1-82e8-854ab0b3d995-ex1', 'c6601e80-b1b2-4eb1-82e8-854ab0b3d995', 'drawer', 'The keys are in the top drawer.', '钥匙在最上面的抽屉里。'),
