  ('f8fa1631-a103-4770-8821-690320e8290a-ex1', 'f8fa1631-a103-4770-8821-690320e8290a', 'ideological', 'The debate had an ideological tone.', '这场辩论带有意识形态色彩。'),
  ('f8fa1631-a103-4770-8821-690320e8290a-ex2', 'f8fa1631-a103-4770-8821-690320e8290a', 'ideological', 'The reform transcended ideological lines, drawing cross-party support.', '这项改革超越了意识形态界限，赢得了跨党派支持。'),
  ('fe1426d2-7b58-437e-96d7-f4231aef2265-ex1', 'fe1426d2-7b58-437e-96d7-f4231aef2265', 'runner', 'The runner crossed the finish line.', '跑步者冲过了终点线。'),
  ('fe1426d2-7b58-437e-96d7-f4231aef2265-ex2', 'fe1426d2-7b58-437e-96d7-f4231aef2265', 'runner', 'The front-runner''s lead narrowed sharply in the final week.', '领跑者的优势在最后一周大幅缩小。'),
  ('d4803f1c-6bab-4b89-91c2-12b3d31f919c-ex1', 'd4803f1c-6bab-4b89-91c2-12b3d31f919c', 'secular', 'It is a secular school.', '这是一所世俗学校。'),
