  ('0ad58d45-c34f-48c3-b335-dec7949590df-ex1', '0ad58d45-c34f-48c3-b335-dec7949590df', 'earthquake', 'The earthquake destroyed many homes.', '地震摧毁了许多房屋。'),
  ('0ad58d45-c34f-48c3-b335-dec7949590df-ex2', '0ad58d45-c34f-48c3-b335-dec7949590df', 'earthquake', 'The earthquake''s epicenter lay within a fault system the survey had mapped.', '地震的震中位于勘测已绘制的断层系统之内。'),
  ('2ff2324b-9533-482a-9d67-022c93fa8abc-ex1', '2ff2324b-9533-482a-9d67-022c93fa8abc', 'pork', 'We had roast pork for dinner.', '我们晚餐吃了烤猪肉。'),
  ('2ff2324b-9533-482a-9d67-022c93fa8abc-ex2', '2ff2324b-9533-482a-9d67-022c93fa8abc', 'pork', 'The traceability rules cover every pork product entering the common market.', '可追溯性规则覆盖进入共同市场的所有猪肉产品。'),
  ('9a44d489-a3bc-4566-ba7f-cbed7a4dc8f2-ex1', '9a44d489-a3bc-4566-ba7f-cbed7a4dc8f2', 'creativity', 'The job requires creativity.', '这份工作需要创造力。'),
  ('9a44d489-a3bc-4566-ba7f-cbed7a4dc8f2-ex2', '9a44d489-a3bc-4566-ba7f-cbed7a4dc8f2', 'creativity', 'The accounting displayed creativity the auditors ultimately refused to endorse.', '这种会计处理别出心裁，审计师最终拒绝认可。'),
  ('cc67a5b1-e508-4f86-b8b6-cd26986ff570-ex1', 'cc67a5b1-e508-4f86-b8b6-cd26986ff570', 'safely', 'Drive safely on the icy road.', '在结冰的路上安全驾驶。'),
  ('cc67a5b1-e508-4f86-b8b6-cd26986ff570-ex2', 'cc67a5b1-e508-4f86-b8b6-cd26986ff570', 'safely', 'One may safely conclude that the safeguards were inadequate from the outset.', '可以有把握地断定，这些保障措施从一开始就不充分。'),
  ('11f26db2-ee5d-41c1-909d-0bc4077672ba-ex1', '11f26db2-ee5d-41c1-909d-0bc4077672ba', 'underlying', 'What is the underlying cause?', '根本原因是什么？'),
  ('11f26db2-ee5d-41c1-909d-0bc4077672ba-ex2', '11f26db2-ee5d-41c1-909d-0bc4077672ba', 'underlying', 'The reforms barely touch the underlying drivers of the affordability crisis.', '这些改革几乎没有触及住房负担危机的深层动因。'),
  ('63777e91-09bd-4ed2-bc32-edbf6466cc71-ex1', '63777e91-09bd-4ed2-bc32-edbf6466cc71', 'dessert', 'Would you like some dessert?', '你想来点甜点吗？'),
  ('63777e91-09bd-4ed2-bc32-edbf6466cc71-ex2', '63777e91-09bd-4ed2-bc32-edbf6466cc71', 'dessert', 'Each faction sought a larger portion before the fiscal dessert was carved up.', '在财政蛋糕被分配之前，各派系都想分得更大一份。'),
  ('19d29ec9-61af-4a77-8e07-7710718bd4a2-ex1', '19d29ec9-61af-4a77-8e07-7710718bd4a2', 'sympathy', 'She expressed her sympathy.', '她表达了同情。'),
  ('19d29ec9-61af-4a77-8e07-7710718bd4a2-ex2', '19d29ec9-61af-4a77-8e07-7710718bd4a2', 'sympathy', 'The court showed little sympathy for a defendant who had concealed material evidence.', '对于隐瞒重要证据的被告，法院几乎不予同情。'),
  ('2779f6e6-b634-44b3-a022-ad71dea87e8d-ex1', '2779f6e6-b634-44b3-a022-ad71dea87e8d', 'fisherman', 'The fisherman cast his net.', '渔夫撒下了网。'),
  ('2779f6e6-b634-44b3-a022-ad71dea87e8d-ex2', '2779f6e6-b634-44b3-a022-ad71dea87e8d', 'fisherman', 'Declining stocks have devastated the livelihoods of small-scale fishermen.', '渔业资源的减少重创了小规模渔民的生计。'),
  ('3a03d469-b067-4a20-97da-3d28afff2985-ex1', '3a03d469-b067-4a20-97da-3d28afff2985', 'incredibly', 'The view was incredibly beautiful.', '景色美得令人难以置信。'),
  ('3a03d469-b067-4a20-97da-3d28afff2985-ex2', '3a03d469-b067-4a20-97da-3d28afff2985', 'incredibly', 'The concealment was incredibly sophisticated, eluding three rounds of audit.', '这种隐瞒手法极其高明，躲过了三轮审计。'),
  ('8c6538ed-3b13-4ad0-b4b7-c4905ce122b9-ex1', '8c6538ed-3b13-4ad0-b4b7-c4905ce122b9', 'isolation', 'The patient was kept in isolation.', '病人被隔离了。'),
  ('8c6538ed-3b13-4ad0-b4b7-c4905ce122b9-ex2', '8c6538ed-3b13-4ad0-b4b7-c4905ce122b9', 'isolation', 'No single measure works in isolation from the broader regulatory framework.', '任何单一措施都无法脱离更广泛的监管框架而单独发挥作用。'),
  ('4ec62d0d-bea4-4f26-beb1-8bac58991f80-ex1', '4ec62d0d-bea4-4f26-beb1-8bac58991f80', 'sock', 'I can''t find my other sock.', '我找不到另一只袜子了。'),
  ('4ec62d0d-bea4-4f26-beb1-8bac58991f80-ex2', '4ec62d0d-bea4-4f26-beb1-8bac58991f80', 'sock', 'The penalty socked the firm with costs scaled to its global revenue.', '这项处罚按其全球营收向该公司施加了高额罚款。'),
  ('862021b6-ff2c-456d-8158-a70358b6be24-ex1', '862021b6-ff2c-456d-8158-a70358b6be24', 'eleven', 'The bus comes at eleven.', '公交车十一点来。'),
  ('862021b6-ff2c-456d-8158-a70358b6be24-ex2', '862021b6-ff2c-456d-8158-a70358b6be24', 'eleven', 'The treaty was ratified by all eleven signatory states within a single session.', '该条约在一个会期内获得全部十一个签署国批准。'),
  ('e3583586-1878-4bbe-9642-6f469e8f9054-ex1', 'e3583586-1878-4bbe-9642-6f469e8f9054', 'sexy', 'That is a sexy new car.', '那是一辆很拉风的新车。'),
  ('e3583586-1878-4bbe-9642-6f469e8f9054-ex2', 'e3583586-1878-4bbe-9642-6f469e8f9054', 'sexy', 'Compliance is rarely sexy, yet its neglect proves spectacularly costly.', '合规鲜少光鲜诱人，但忽视它的代价却极其高昂。'),
  ('10fb349d-5f8d-4347-84b8-05a2dc840016-ex1', '10fb349d-5f8d-4347-84b8-05a2dc840016', 'entrepreneur', 'She is a successful entrepreneur.', '她是一位成功的企业家。'),
  ('10fb349d-5f8d-4347-84b8-05a2dc840016-ex2', '10fb349d-5f8d-4347-84b8-05a2dc840016', 'entrepreneur', 'The reforms aim to lower entry barriers facing first-time entrepreneurs.', '这些改革旨在降低初次创业者面临的准入门槛。'),
  ('4aab359f-8c3f-4c24-8507-309ebc855f13-ex1', '4aab359f-8c3f-4c24-8507-309ebc855f13', 'syndrome', 'The doctor diagnosed a rare syndrome.', '医生诊断出一种罕见的综合征。'),
  ('4aab359f-8c3f-4c24-8507-309ebc855f13-ex2', '4aab359f-8c3f-4c24-8507-309ebc855f13', 'syndrome', 'The not-invented-here syndrome delayed adoption of proven safeguards.', '“非我所创”的排斥心理拖延了对成熟保障措施的采用。'),
  ('e5b14b1a-6799-4bef-8880-7875ee696104-ex1', 'e5b14b1a-6799-4bef-8880-7875ee696104', 'bureau', 'He works at the news bureau.', '他在新闻分社工作。'),
  ('e5b14b1a-6799-4bef-8880-7875ee696104-ex2', 'e5b14b1a-6799-4bef-8880-7875ee696104', 'bureau', 'The bureau exceeded its mandate by imposing requirements never authorized.', '该局施加了从未授权的要求，超越了其职权范围。'),
  ('b48985ef-874b-42aa-83c1-89716d50b6e0-ex1', 'b48985ef-874b-42aa-83c1-89716d50b6e0', 'workplace', 'Safety in the workplace is important.', '工作场所的安全很重要。'),
  ('b48985ef-874b-42aa-83c1-89716d50b6e0-ex2', 'b48985ef-874b-42aa-83c1-89716d50b6e0', 'workplace', 'The statute mandates a workplace free from harassment and discrimination.', '该法规要求工作场所不得存在骚扰和歧视。'),
  ('bc061a85-e5cc-4b00-a94b-38649fcb88c6-ex1', 'bc061a85-e5cc-4b00-a94b-38649fcb88c6', 'ambition', 'She has great ambition.', '她志向远大。'),
  ('bc061a85-e5cc-4b00-a94b-38649fcb88c6-ex2', 'bc061a85-e5cc-4b00-a94b-38649fcb88c6', 'ambition', 'The accord''s ambition outstripped the members'' willingness to enforce it.', '该协定的雄心超出了成员国执行它的意愿。'),
  ('cca8400a-7edb-4c92-a4c1-14cc9d3febec-ex1', 'cca8400a-7edb-4c92-a4c1-14cc9d3febec', 'touchdown', 'The team scored a touchdown.', '球队达阵得分。'),
  ('cca8400a-7edb-4c92-a4c1-14cc9d3febec-ex2', 'cca8400a-7edb-4c92-a4c1-14cc9d3febec', 'touchdown', 'The negotiations finally reached touchdown after months of stalemate.', '经过数月僵持，谈判终于尘埃落定。'),
  ('164d5ba7-4cfd-4434-a9e0-dc0897d73ecb-ex1', '164d5ba7-4cfd-4434-a9e0-dc0897d73ecb', 'utilize', 'We utilize solar energy at home.', '我们家里利用太阳能。'),
  ('164d5ba7-4cfd-4434-a9e0-dc0897d73ecb-ex2', '164d5ba7-4cfd-4434-a9e0-dc0897d73ecb', 'utilize', 'The auditors utilize sampling methodologies validated by the oversight board.', '审计师采用经监督委员会验证的抽样方法。'),
  ('203697cd-d9af-465e-ac9b-5d606d694150-ex1', '203697cd-d9af-465e-ac9b-5d606d694150', 'breeze', 'A gentle breeze cooled the room.', '一阵微风让房间凉爽下来。'),
  ('203697cd-d9af-465e-ac9b-5d606d694150-ex2', '203697cd-d9af-465e-ac9b-5d606d694150', 'breeze', 'The early stages proved a breeze, but enforcement became the real test.', '早期阶段轻而易举，但执行才是真正的考验。'),
