  ('74ff42a8-2eb9-4bb1-ab1e-eb232b0c8d0d-ex2', '74ff42a8-2eb9-4bb1-ab1e-eb232b0c8d0d', 'ambitious', 'The summit produced the most ambitious climate commitments ever endorsed.', '此次峰会产生了有史以来最具雄心的气候承诺。'),
  ('6a95283c-47a5-471f-a0a8-1a4601d1cd44-ex1', '6a95283c-47a5-471f-a0a8-1a4601d1cd44', 'Christianity', 'He studies the history of Christianity.', '他研究基督教的历史。'),
  ('6a95283c-47a5-471f-a0a8-1a4601d1cd44-ex2', '6a95283c-47a5-471f-a0a8-1a4601d1cd44', 'Christianity', 'The manuscript illuminates the spread of Christianity across the eastern Mediterranean.', '这份手稿揭示了基督教在地中海东部的传播。'),
