  ('08161da5-9abb-4b73-a7fb-a494d5387241-ex1', '08161da5-9abb-4b73-a7fb-a494d5387241', 'rolling', 'The ball kept rolling down the hill.', '球一直往山下滚。'),
  ('08161da5-9abb-4b73-a7fb-a494d5387241-ex2', '08161da5-9abb-4b73-a7fb-a494d5387241', 'rolling', 'The framework imposes a rolling program of stress testing.', '该框架实施了一套滚动式的压力测试计划。'),
  ('1b148c6a-433a-4357-96a9-d1d53bcaf246-ex1', '1b148c6a-433a-4357-96a9-d1d53bcaf246', 'aesthetic', 'The room has a minimalist aesthetic.', '这个房间是极简主义美学风格。'),
  ('1b148c6a-433a-4357-96a9-d1d53bcaf246-ex2', '1b148c6a-433a-4357-96a9-d1d53bcaf246', 'aesthetic', 'The aesthetic merit of the work did not exempt it from defamation analysis.', '作品的美学价值并不能使其免于诽谤分析。'),
  ('f2075475-047e-43f9-9945-9478809aec74-ex1', 'f2075475-047e-43f9-9945-9478809aec74', 'spell', 'Can you spell your name?', '你能拼写你的名字吗？'),
  ('f2075475-047e-43f9-9945-9478809aec74-ex2', 'f2075475-047e-43f9-9945-9478809aec74', 'spell', 'The disclosures spelled the end of a reputation built over decades.', '这些披露宣告了一段数十年声誉的终结。'),
  ('3517ef48-ca4c-4a2b-aabd-332d03d377e0-ex1', '3517ef48-ca4c-4a2b-aabd-332d03d377e0', 'insert', 'Insert the coin into the slot.', '把硬币投进投币口。'),
