  ('30532d3b-c9bb-465d-bbc7-0259817c8352-ex1', '30532d3b-c9bb-465d-bbc7-0259817c8352', 'waist', 'The water came up to my waist.', '水深及腰。'),
  ('30532d3b-c9bb-465d-bbc7-0259817c8352-ex2', '30532d3b-c9bb-465d-bbc7-0259817c8352', 'waist', 'The company tightened its belt around its waist after the downturn.', '经济下行之后，该公司勒紧了裤腰带。'),
  ('d80e4bad-da53-4aa1-af8e-87ca9a56f2a4-ex1', 'd80e4bad-da53-4aa1-af8e-87ca9a56f2a4', 'considering', 'Considering the price, it is a good deal.', '考虑到价格，这是笔划算的买卖。'),
  ('d80e4bad-da53-4aa1-af8e-87ca9a56f2a4-ex2', 'd80e4bad-da53-4aa1-af8e-87ca9a56f2a4', 'considering', 'Considering the magnitude of the exposure, intervention was unavoidable.', '鉴于风险敞口之大，干预已不可避免。'),
  ('07dc1610-62dc-4f1b-9eed-e731eb99a4f9-ex1', '07dc1610-62dc-4f1b-9eed-e731eb99a4f9', 'expected', 'The expected guests arrived on time.', '预期的客人准时到达。'),
  ('07dc1610-62dc-4f1b-9eed-e731eb99a4f9-ex2', '07dc1610-62dc-4f1b-9eed-e731eb99a4f9', 'expected', 'The reforms produced gains far below the level the projections had expected.', '这些改革的成效远低于预测所预期的水平。'),
  ('7f6bb990-a48a-4186-8ae4-6e6cf68a3ddc-ex1', '7f6bb990-a48a-4186-8ae4-6e6cf68a3ddc', 'excluding', 'The price is fifty dollars, excluding tax.', '价格是五十美元，不含税。'),
  ('7f6bb990-a48a-4186-8ae4-6e6cf68a3ddc-ex2', '7f6bb990-a48a-4186-8ae4-6e6cf68a3ddc', 'excluding', 'Excluding the one-off charge, earnings remained broadly flat year on year.', '剔除一次性费用后，盈利同比大体持平。'),
  ('05db2579-bc0a-4f03-808a-2db36dc2c497-ex1', '05db2579-bc0a-4f03-808a-2db36dc2c497', 'lion', 'The lion is the king of beasts.', '狮子是百兽之王。'),
  ('05db2579-bc0a-4f03-808a-2db36dc2c497-ex2', '05db2579-bc0a-4f03-808a-2db36dc2c497', 'lion', 'The firm took the lion''s share of a market it effectively monopolized.', '该公司在它实际垄断的市场中占据了绝大部分份额。'),
  ('1e174870-3b07-4c6b-b51a-61d368014fd9-ex1', '1e174870-3b07-4c6b-b51a-61d368014fd9', 'gone', 'By the time I arrived, she was gone.', '我到的时候她已经走了。'),
  ('1e174870-3b07-4c6b-b51a-61d368014fd9-ex2', '1e174870-3b07-4c6b-b51a-61d368014fd9', 'gone', 'By the time regulators intervened, the moment for prevention had long gone.', '等到监管机构介入时，预防的时机早已错过。'),
  ('785e3222-88af-4b56-8b1d-667b3925f904-ex1', '785e3222-88af-4b56-8b1d-667b3925f904', 'minus', 'Five minus two is three.', '五减二等于三。'),
  ('785e3222-88af-4b56-8b1d-667b3925f904-ex2', '785e3222-88af-4b56-8b1d-667b3925f904', 'minus', 'The temperature plunged to minus twenty during the record cold snap.', '在创纪录的寒潮中，气温骤降至零下二十度。'),
  ('c44e8d77-f2a2-41d6-8d2f-c3821c646e47-ex1', 'c44e8d77-f2a2-41d6-8d2f-c3821c646e47', 'accomplishment', 'Finishing the marathon was an accomplishment.', '完成马拉松是一项成就。'),
  ('c44e8d77-f2a2-41d6-8d2f-c3821c646e47-ex2', 'c44e8d77-f2a2-41d6-8d2f-c3821c646e47', 'accomplishment', 'The accord stands as the signal accomplishment of a decade of diplomacy.', '该协定是十年外交最显著的成就。'),
  ('bc0ae921-1580-47f8-9880-b6430fd4cb58-ex1', 'bc0ae921-1580-47f8-9880-b6430fd4cb58', 'royal', 'They visited the royal palace.', '他们参观了皇宫。'),
  ('bc0ae921-1580-47f8-9880-b6430fd4cb58-ex2', 'bc0ae921-1580-47f8-9880-b6430fd4cb58', 'royal', 'The royal charter conferred privileges the company later struggled to justify.', '皇家特许状授予的特权后来令该公司难以自圆其说。'),
  ('f1d31189-ccbd-49b8-aa94-34be8000a75d-ex1', 'f1d31189-ccbd-49b8-aa94-34be8000a75d', 'pending', 'The decision is still pending.', '决定仍未确定。'),
  ('f1d31189-ccbd-49b8-aa94-34be8000a75d-ex2', 'f1d31189-ccbd-49b8-aa94-34be8000a75d', 'pending', 'The injunction remains in force pending the constitutional appeal.', '在宪法上诉审结之前，该禁令持续有效。'),
  ('6fb7c2ef-40eb-4a44-a1dd-cc9ceb055d91-ex1', '6fb7c2ef-40eb-4a44-a1dd-cc9ceb055d91', 'times', 'Three times four is twelve.', '三乘以四等于十二。'),
  ('6fb7c2ef-40eb-4a44-a1dd-cc9ceb055d91-ex2', '6fb7c2ef-40eb-4a44-a1dd-cc9ceb055d91', 'times', 'The losses ran to many times the firm''s reported capital reserves.', '亏损达到该公司账面资本储备的许多倍。'),
  ('784af37e-2a19-485c-b416-da4137af5ab9-ex1', '784af37e-2a19-485c-b416-da4137af5ab9', 'panic', 'Don''t panic; help is coming.', '别慌，救援就来了。'),
  ('784af37e-2a19-485c-b416-da4137af5ab9-ex2', '784af37e-2a19-485c-b416-da4137af5ab9', 'panic', 'The disclosure triggered a panic that froze interbank lending overnight.', '这次披露引发的恐慌一夜之间冻结了银行间拆借。'),
  ('a228d9fe-adaf-4906-a042-200388857038-ex1', 'a228d9fe-adaf-4906-a042-200388857038', 'underneath', 'The cat is hiding underneath the bed.', '猫藏在床底下。'),
  ('a228d9fe-adaf-4906-a042-200388857038-ex2', 'a228d9fe-adaf-4906-a042-200388857038', 'underneath', 'Underneath the procedural dispute lay a deeper contest over authority.', '程序之争的背后是一场关于权限的更深层较量。'),
  ('e305c952-8f6b-4230-990a-eb32961facf3-ex1', 'e305c952-8f6b-4230-990a-eb32961facf3', 'agile', 'The cat is small and agile.', '这只猫又小又敏捷。'),
  ('e305c952-8f6b-4230-990a-eb32961facf3-ex2', 'e305c952-8f6b-4230-990a-eb32961facf3', 'agile', 'The team adopted an agile workflow to ship features in short iterations.', '团队采用敏捷工作流程，以短迭代周期交付功能。'),
  ('1ec55e6b-9df1-48dc-ace2-c72fc6920e3d-ex1', '1ec55e6b-9df1-48dc-ace2-c72fc6920e3d', 'alert', 'The guard stayed alert all night.', '警卫整夜保持警惕。'),
  ('1ec55e6b-9df1-48dc-ace2-c72fc6920e3d-ex2', '1ec55e6b-9df1-48dc-ace2-c72fc6920e3d', 'alert', 'The agency issued an alert pending confirmation of the contamination''s extent.', '在污染范围得到确认之前，该机构发布了警报。'),
  ('c0d3df05-be1f-41e6-a6cb-49e519745fb0-ex1', 'c0d3df05-be1f-41e6-a6cb-49e519745fb0', 'crush', 'Don''t crush the flowers.', '别把花压坏了。'),
  ('c0d3df05-be1f-41e6-a6cb-49e519745fb0-ex2', 'c0d3df05-be1f-41e6-a6cb-49e519745fb0', 'crush', 'Cheap imports threatened to crush domestic producers lacking comparable subsidies.', '廉价进口商品可能压垮缺乏同等补贴的国内生产商。'),
  ('b18f11a4-5cd3-4301-9b5b-a7f34f96e2b1-ex1', 'b18f11a4-5cd3-4301-9b5b-a7f34f96e2b1', 'actively', 'She actively participates in class.', '她积极参与课堂。'),
  ('b18f11a4-5cd3-4301-9b5b-a7f34f96e2b1-ex2', 'b18f11a4-5cd3-4301-9b5b-a7f34f96e2b1', 'actively', 'The regulator actively monitors concentrations approaching the statutory threshold.', '监管机构主动监测接近法定门槛的集中行为。'),
  ('ee30a5d5-298d-4580-b536-09e439ffc8d3-ex1', 'ee30a5d5-298d-4580-b536-09e439ffc8d3', 'algorithm', 'The app uses a simple algorithm.', '这个应用使用了一个简单的算法。'),
  ('ee30a5d5-298d-4580-b536-09e439ffc8d3-ex2', 'ee30a5d5-298d-4580-b536-09e439ffc8d3', 'algorithm', 'The directive requires platforms to disclose how their ranking algorithm operates.', '该指令要求平台披露其排序算法的运作方式。'),
  ('22f78fc7-9107-4f31-8c6a-e2690fab9d27-ex1', '22f78fc7-9107-4f31-8c6a-e2690fab9d27', 'cliff', 'The house sits on a cliff above the sea.', '房子坐落在海边的悬崖上。'),
  ('22f78fc7-9107-4f31-8c6a-e2690fab9d27-ex2', '22f78fc7-9107-4f31-8c6a-e2690fab9d27', 'cliff', 'The economy approached a fiscal cliff as temporary measures expired.', '随着临时措施到期，经济逼近财政悬崖。'),
  ('2c170362-251f-4cfd-bc0f-80911c54a47e-ex1', '2c170362-251f-4cfd-bc0f-80911c54a47e', 'async', 'The function runs in an async manner.', '这个函数以异步方式运行。'),
  ('2c170362-251f-4cfd-bc0f-80911c54a47e-ex2', '2c170362-251f-4cfd-bc0f-80911c54a47e', 'async', 'Refactoring the handler to be async eliminated the blocking calls that stalled requests.', '将处理器重构为异步消除了导致请求阻塞的同步调用。'),
  ('350c36d8-8c83-40dd-a087-ef828c2f2095-ex1', '350c36d8-8c83-40dd-a087-ef828c2f2095', 'backend', 'He works on the backend of the app.', '他负责应用的后端。'),
  ('350c36d8-8c83-40dd-a087-ef828c2f2095-ex2', '350c36d8-8c83-40dd-a087-ef828c2f2095', 'backend', 'The outage was traced to a backend service that silently dropped requests under load.', '故障被定位到一个在高负载下悄然丢弃请求的后端服务。'),
  ('bdf0b25a-8473-42af-a27b-91d76f5b5698-ex1', 'bdf0b25a-8473-42af-a27b-91d76f5b5698', 'minimal', 'The damage was minimal.', '损失很小。'),
  ('bdf0b25a-8473-42af-a27b-91d76f5b5698-ex2', 'bdf0b25a-8473-42af-a27b-91d76f5b5698', 'minimal', 'The elegance of the solution lies in deriving deep results from minimal assumptions.', '该解决方案的精妙之处在于从最少的假设推出深刻的结果。'),
  ('b1c4bd24-dfa6-4b73-bba3-624f6adc9fce-ex1', 'b1c4bd24-dfa6-4b73-bba3-624f6adc9fce', 'backup', 'Always keep a backup of your files.', '务必备份你的文件。'),
  ('b1c4bd24-dfa6-4b73-bba3-624f6adc9fce-ex2', 'b1c4bd24-dfa6-4b73-bba3-624f6adc9fce', 'backup', 'The emergency facility served as a backup against shocks the model could not predict.', '这项紧急安排是抵御模型无法预测的冲击的后备措施。')
INSERT INTO vocab_examples (id, vocabulary_id, word, sentence_en, sentence_zh) VALUES
  ('c84a281c-992b-4653-b7be-4692c1462351-ex1', 'c84a281c-992b-4653-b7be-4692c1462351', 'cord', 'The charger cord is too short.', '充电线太短了。'),
  ('c84a281c-992b-4653-b7be-4692c1462351-ex2', 'c84a281c-992b-4653-b7be-4692c1462351', 'cord', 'Investigators followed the financial cord linking the shell entities to one beneficiary.', '调查人员沿着将空壳实体与单一受益人相连的资金脉络追查。'),
  ('301ac214-604a-431c-9dfb-5a24bdae5780-ex1', '301ac214-604a-431c-9dfb-5a24bdae5780', 'bandwidth', 'Video streaming uses a lot of bandwidth.', '视频流媒体会消耗大量带宽。'),
  ('301ac214-604a-431c-9dfb-5a24bdae5780-ex2', '301ac214-604a-431c-9dfb-5a24bdae5780', 'bandwidth', 'The team lacked the bandwidth to address the backlog before the release.', '团队没有足够的精力在发布前处理积压工作。'),
  ('5aa45055-55be-44a2-99a8-19cce75ef757-ex1', '5aa45055-55be-44a2-99a8-19cce75ef757', 'fortunately', 'Fortunately, no one was hurt.', '幸运的是，没有人受伤。'),
  ('5aa45055-55be-44a2-99a8-19cce75ef757-ex2', '5aa45055-55be-44a2-99a8-19cce75ef757', 'fortunately', 'Fortunately, the contingency plan activated before the disruption spread further.', '幸运的是，应急预案在中断进一步扩散前就已启动。'),
  ('01105d36-c7f7-4fe6-8a35-b5667e63fdfe-ex1', '01105d36-c7f7-4fe6-8a35-b5667e63fdfe', 'binary', 'Computers store data in binary.', '计算机以二进制存储数据。'),
  ('01105d36-c7f7-4fe6-8a35-b5667e63fdfe-ex2', '01105d36-c7f7-4fe6-8a35-b5667e63fdfe', 'binary', 'The choice is not binary; intermediate regulatory options remain available.', '这一选择并非非此即彼，仍存在折中的监管选项。'),
  ('bf730865-9b85-4dfa-985c-6858adaa70b2-ex1', 'bf730865-9b85-4dfa-985c-6858adaa70b2', 'cocaine', 'Cocaine is an illegal drug.', '可卡因是一种非法毒品。'),
  ('bf730865-9b85-4dfa-985c-6858adaa70b2-ex2', 'bf730865-9b85-4dfa-985c-6858adaa70b2', 'cocaine', 'Customs intercepted a consignment of cocaine concealed within the cargo.', '海关截获了一批藏匿在货物中的可卡因。'),
  ('0ca905b7-dc7c-4070-8cfd-8e0ac7371898-ex1', '0ca905b7-dc7c-4070-8cfd-8e0ac7371898', 'boolean', 'The flag is a boolean value.', '这个标志是一个布尔值。'),
  ('0ca905b7-dc7c-4070-8cfd-8e0ac7371898-ex2', '0ca905b7-dc7c-4070-8cfd-8e0ac7371898', 'boolean', 'The function returns a boolean indicating whether validation succeeded.', '该函数返回一个布尔值，表示校验是否成功。'),
  ('f5f333d5-f275-4d94-ad5f-3b87af782a96-ex1', 'f5f333d5-f275-4d94-ad5f-3b87af782a96', 'illusion', 'The magician created an illusion.', '魔术师制造了一个幻象。'),
  ('f5f333d5-f275-4d94-ad5f-3b87af782a96-ex2', 'f5f333d5-f275-4d94-ad5f-3b87af782a96', 'illusion', 'The reported stability was an illusion masking accumulating systemic stress.', '所报告的稳定只是掩盖系统性压力累积的假象。'),
  ('2ab71eee-956c-4a0c-bde8-ab3e5a59d02a-ex1', '2ab71eee-956c-4a0c-bde8-ab3e5a59d02a', 'buffer', 'A buffer of trees blocks the noise.', '一排树木缓冲了噪音。'),
  ('2ab71eee-956c-4a0c-bde8-ab3e5a59d02a-ex2', '2ab71eee-956c-4a0c-bde8-ab3e5a59d02a', 'buffer', 'Capital buffers accumulate during expansions to absorb downturn losses.', '资本缓冲在扩张期积累，用以吸收衰退期的损失。'),
  ('822ecf4d-ab37-45a5-9fe2-e61ae2597dd2-ex1', '822ecf4d-ab37-45a5-9fe2-e61ae2597dd2', 'anonymous', 'The donor wished to remain anonymous.', '捐赠者希望保持匿名。'),
  ('822ecf4d-ab37-45a5-9fe2-e61ae2597dd2-ex2', '822ecf4d-ab37-45a5-9fe2-e61ae2597dd2', 'anonymous', 'An anonymous tip prompted the inspection that uncovered the violations.', '一条匿名举报促成了那次发现违规行为的检查。'),
  ('1a1b1b44-66cc-47fd-9b64-04e8a713ccc9-ex1', '1a1b1b44-66cc-47fd-9b64-04e8a713ccc9', 'byte', 'A kilobyte is a thousand bytes.', '一千字节等于一千个字节。'),
  ('1a1b1b44-66cc-47fd-9b64-04e8a713ccc9-ex2', '1a1b1b44-66cc-47fd-9b64-04e8a713ccc9', 'byte', 'Every byte of the transmitted data is encrypted in transit under the protocol.', '根据该协议，传输中的每一字节数据都经过加密。'),
  ('5f8a89af-17ec-4ce5-a87a-828409e9785b-ex1', '5f8a89af-17ec-4ce5-a87a-828409e9785b', 'tolerate', 'I can''t tolerate this noise.', '我受不了这种噪音。'),
  ('5f8a89af-17ec-4ce5-a87a-828409e9785b-ex2', '5f8a89af-17ec-4ce5-a87a-828409e9785b', 'tolerate', 'The framework will not tolerate breaches that imperil systemic stability.', '该框架绝不容忍危及系统稳定的违规行为。'),
  ('8caf6095-2b40-4ee0-90fa-4be749b4b5cc-ex1', '8caf6095-2b40-4ee0-90fa-4be749b4b5cc', 'cache', 'Clear the browser cache to fix it.', '清除浏览器缓存即可解决。'),
  ('8caf6095-2b40-4ee0-90fa-4be749b4b5cc-ex2', '8caf6095-2b40-4ee0-90fa-4be749b4b5cc', 'cache', 'The stale cache served outdated prices long after the source had updated.', '在数据源已更新很久之后，过时的缓存仍在提供陈旧的价格。'),
  ('bd0c75f4-88ae-4889-b7f5-586204911893-ex1', 'bd0c75f4-88ae-4889-b7f5-586204911893', 'appreciation', 'She showed her appreciation with a card.', '她用一张卡片表达感激。'),
  ('bd0c75f4-88ae-4889-b7f5-586204911893-ex2', 'bd0c75f4-88ae-4889-b7f5-586204911893', 'appreciation', 'The currency''s appreciation eroded the competitiveness of export industries.', '本币升值削弱了出口产业的竞争力。'),
  ('5611cd75-52f9-429e-958d-f994d42e52b8-ex1', '5611cd75-52f9-429e-958d-f994d42e52b8', 'compile', 'The teacher compiled a reading list.', '老师整理了一份阅读书单。'),
  ('5611cd75-52f9-429e-958d-f994d42e52b8-ex2', '5611cd75-52f9-429e-958d-f994d42e52b8', 'compile', 'The code failed to compile because of an unresolved dependency.', '由于一个未解决的依赖项，代码编译失败。'),
  ('8d2f2dad-4dd8-4e23-8e3c-c0b3970385ff-ex1', '8d2f2dad-4dd8-4e23-8e3c-c0b3970385ff', 'commissioner', 'The commissioner opened the hearing.', '专员宣布听证会开始。'),
  ('8d2f2dad-4dd8-4e23-8e3c-c0b3970385ff-ex2', '8d2f2dad-4dd8-4e23-8e3c-c0b3970385ff', 'commissioner', 'The commissioner exercises investigative powers including compulsory disclosure.', '专员行使包括强制披露在内的调查权。'),
  ('5203ff16-d922-428b-9c29-8e9850a27e6c-ex1', '5203ff16-d922-428b-9c29-8e9850a27e6c', 'compiler', 'The compiler reported an error.', '编译器报了一个错误。'),
  ('5203ff16-d922-428b-9c29-8e9850a27e6c-ex2', '5203ff16-d922-428b-9c29-8e9850a27e6c', 'compiler', 'The compiler flagged the type mismatch before the code ever ran.', '编译器在代码运行之前就标出了类型不匹配。'),
  ('811977e9-45ed-4b56-bcbf-0b72638806d1-ex1', '811977e9-45ed-4b56-bcbf-0b72638806d1', 'flexibility', 'Yoga improves flexibility.', '瑜伽能提高柔韧性。'),
  ('811977e9-45ed-4b56-bcbf-0b72638806d1-ex2', '811977e9-45ed-4b56-bcbf-0b72638806d1', 'flexibility', 'The framework retains flexibility to adapt as financial innovation evolves.', '该框架保留了随金融创新演进而调整的灵活性。'),
  ('fd4f7089-3411-4ac9-bd9f-97a0f66a085a-ex1', 'fd4f7089-3411-4ac9-bd9f-97a0f66a085a', 'configure', 'You need to configure the router first.', '你需要先配置路由器。'),
  ('fd4f7089-3411-4ac9-bd9f-97a0f66a085a-ex2', 'fd4f7089-3411-4ac9-bd9f-97a0f66a085a', 'configure', 'The system was configured to log every access to the privileged records.', '系统被配置为记录对特权记录的每一次访问。'),
  ('16008e21-ac7c-4b3d-9b15-8674904727f2-ex1', '16008e21-ac7c-4b3d-9b15-8674904727f2', 'instructional', 'The video is purely instructional.', '这段视频纯粹是教学性质的。'),
  ('16008e21-ac7c-4b3d-9b15-8674904727f2-ex2', '16008e21-ac7c-4b3d-9b15-8674904727f2', 'instructional', 'The reform redirects funding toward instructional rather than administrative roles.', '这项改革将经费转向教学岗位而非行政岗位。'),
